Description:
In the sewers you find a large vault door in one wall. Surprisingly, the door is open and leads underground.

When you go down, the cold becomes unbearable. You take a quick look and see a large tunnel, along which you can see a lot of gold and shards. It seems that more objects were kept here, but now the vault is practically empty.

You go back up quickly so as not to freeze. You could go down again for the gold and shards, but the further you go, the more danger it entails.
DescriptionAction: How far do you want to go?
